input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT \`School Name\`, \`Enrollment (K-12)\`, \`Free Meal Count (K-12)\`, \`Free Meal Count (K-12)\` / \`Enrollment (K-12)\` AS eligible_free_rate FROM frpm WHERE \`Enrollment (K-12)\` IS NOT NULL AND \`Enrollment (K-12)\` > 0 ORDER BY \`Enrollment (K-12)\` DESC LIMIT 15;"
